lemma subtyping_append: assumes "CT \<turnstile>+ Cs <: Ds" and "CT \<turnstile> C <: D" shows "CT \<turnstile>+ (Cs@[C]) <: (Ds@[D])"
using assms
by (induct rule:subtypings.induct) (auto intro:subtypings.intros)
